      </div>
      <div class="qbpb-content">
        <div class="qbpb-eyebrow">🍚 Chef's Special</div>
        <div class="qbpb-title">BIRYANI<br><em>149/-</em></div>
        <div class="qbpb-subtitle">Aromatic · Fresh · Authentic<br>Delivered hot to your door</div>
        <span class="qbpb-badge">🛒 Order Now</span>
